@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3000
@apiToken = change-me

### 1) List survey responses (default pagination: page=1, per_page=25)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2) List survey responses with explicit pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?page=0&per_page=100
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3) List survey responses page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?page=2&per_page=25
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4) Filter by exact date
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?date=2022-01-20
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5) Filter by inclusive range (from + to)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?from=2022-01-20&to=2022-01-22
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6) Filter with only from
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?from=2022-01-20
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7) Filter with only to
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?to=2022-01-21
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8) Invalid: date mixed with from/to (expected 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/survey_responses?date=2022-01-20&from=2022-01-01&to=2022-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{apiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
